{"tid":2226562,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【鬼同你上位】34F湯沛宜操出蜜桃臀 晒八月十五賀中秋","createTime":"2020-10-02T06:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T14:39:44.000Z","uid":44730,"like":37,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"354c547ac84fd2ec80153670711e4b2ef5acc5d0","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"湯沛宜近日在ViuTV探靈真人騷《鬼同你上位》表現相當出位，性感Bra Top漏奶探靈，F奶幾乎奪衫而出，睇見觀眾心驚驚。湯沛宜唔止胸狠，近來更苦練蜜桃臀，正值中秋之際，湯沛宜趷蘿騷成果，賀中秋佳節祝大家臀臀圓圓﹗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9611e60b-4901-4ff8-b056-4240f897d746_10070183265f76b03bb79f9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F9611e60b-4901-4ff8-b056-4240f897d746_10070183265f76b03bb79f9.jpeg&h=40b6bff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯沛宜F奶上圍身材驕人，不時在IG晒身材。"},{"pid":"0a845c9d375ac0010dbec112acc75f4af9e9c738","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">蕩奶探靈膽大過人：「驚冇錢多過驚鬼﹗」</span><br />\n<br />\n29歲湯沛宜要入行上位決心相當大，16年參加ViuTV選美節目《美選D.n.A》入圍八強，18年參加過港姐首輪面試被foul，翌年參選健美比賽，擁34F驕人身材的湯沛宜，最近參加ViuTV《鬼同你上位》蕩奶探靈，惹火又出位，被指最膽生毛，為了參加節目獲得的五位數酬勞，湯沛宜坦言為了生計，鬼都唔驚，是家中經濟支柱的湯沛宜直言驚冇錢多過驚鬼，最想《鬼同你上位》有得添食﹗"},{"pid":"d58cb82ef20c82d93b7721644a5ea60e8587892f","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":26,"dislike":94,"score":-68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/cc99d78b-55d7-4674-a2da-483a202b7830_2007564065f76b028abb4e-1024x1000.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fcc99d78b-55d7-4674-a2da-483a202b7830_2007564065f76b028abb4e-1024x1000.jpeg&h=95f0be1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯沛宜近來苦練蜜桃臀，趁在中秋佳節大騷成果，相當應節，成功吸like。"},{"pid":"bf4765924bed563dab5cd0668434f5fb049f231b","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">出股惑引網民</span><br />\n<br />\n湯沛宜本身是一名健身教練，近來密操男士女士大愛的蜜桃臀，趁在中秋佳節，晒八月十五同大家賀中秋，相當應節，成功吸引不少網民來「賞月」，有網民留言：「一張相咁少﹗」，湯沛宜即回覆：「要慢慢出，你哋先會期待。」咁識玩，網民都留言話成個假期會密切留意住湯沛宜IG，等再出圖，另外，湯沛宜又教大家如何練成蜜桃臀，親自教路指主要靠深蹲。"},{"pid":"0d11b44ba279fe866ba4e688832dab997caf1f33","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":18,"dislike":29,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/toto_tongpuiyee_82337833_1009495842767573_2465140838960852040_n_4634824485f76b0529c7eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Ftoto_tongpuiyee_82337833_1009495842767573_2465140838960852040_n_4634824485f76b0529c7eb.jpg&h=f28afcbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯沛宜在IG有不少性感照，自拍露南半球，相當惹火，在《鬼同你上位》亦大方晒奶上鏡，是八位參賽者中最出位的一個。"},{"pid":"10fb66f7b4e52617746b30d6b686f9d89237f710","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":20,"dislike":82,"score":-62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">女星出股惑 麥明詩28歲</span><br />\n<br />\n過往大台女星每逢有劇見街，為宣傳佢哋會話收視超過幾多點就以泳裝示人、報答觀眾云云。依家社交媒體咁發達，三點式照片真係day day有得look啦！有人喜歡賣弄豐滿上圍，但有時刻意而為反不及欲蓋彌彰來得誘惑。以下一班美女似乎悟出此道理，「股」惑制勝！暫別娛樂圈嘅麥明詩，酷愛潛水等水上活動，10A港姐果然識玩，偶然出吓「股」 惑，近排 「林作西裝事件」 真係太倒胃，睇番佢前度條氣即時順番晒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CSPax5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCSPax5p.jpg&h=5c6fffd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4af20dc9efed4e14a26caa82c43f9126bf5fcd5d","tid":2226562,"uid":33059,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"又幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3e7020aa49c86e4ae66ec55e251974751228ea","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":82,"dislike":20,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"陳欣妍27歲<br />\n<br />\n喺ViuTV 節目《美女郊遊遊》中，陳欣妍以性感山系造型亮相而大受網民關注，支持佢多啲去沙灘、泳池大解放，起碼唔使餵蚊先啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xiHSMqE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxiHSMqE.jpg&h=3f3c2439&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12e15d28a9423f9da2ef2a17c117ce563f305967","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":24,"dislike":98,"score":-74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"佘詩曼45歲<br />\n<br />\n一早上晒位嘅佘詩曼，絕對唔使靠泳裝照吸like，難得著上泳衣騷少少，呢類型相片隨時可一不可再！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWiKCxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWiKCxG.jpg&h=ba1e5469&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9942e6b5187dfd69ce05374cb1547091623e392","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":168,"score":-162,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"龔嘉欣30歲<br />\n<br />\n可能龔嘉欣都深明自己並非有「鬼影變幻球」可出賣嗰種type，佢嘅事業唔係靠事業線，艷陽下季節限定靚 「股」 照，成功draw attention！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTnvx6j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTnvx6j.jpg&h=c6f8ca41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2b97df296af63787d60585c8022ab0db5794ddb","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":88,"score":-80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"G.E.M. 28歲<br />\n<br />\n台上台下運動量極高嘅G.E.M.鄧紫棋，身形 fit 到漏，隨意一張坐喺泳池邊嘅大露背泳衣照，透出半股，物以稀為貴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8KqmZX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8KqmZX.jpg&h=ea09157f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb5e8c969f2f313f7022e99fb616f6e57135de45","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":61,"score":-58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"楊柳青 32歲<br />\n<br />\n模特兒出身嘅楊柳青，因參演TVB台慶劇《溏心風暴3》 、 《解決師》而為人所認識，身為泰拳愛好者，楊柳青慢慢轉型為動作演員，見佢練習時經常要起飛腿，難怪下盤勁fit啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qc2Lm0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQc2Lm0q.jpg&h=1211d50c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc46bd2308708b4a0b2e8e78fb8c3929bf5586fc","tid":2226562,"uid":379117,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:02:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f0a7f1bf9a32f80d786db158a890fd59cbbd8e3","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":99,"dislike":59,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"林芊妤 30歲<br />\n<br />\n呢位瑜伽導師日操夜操，玲瓏浮凸線條盡現，難怪一班連登仔見親林芊妤都話想瘋狂飲 coffee 囉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jojqm04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJojqm04.jpg&h=19d58d16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"149d0a0a01b95a136edc6b231905f2ef839ba3c2","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":171,"score":-165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"連詩雅 32歲<br />\n<br />\n十五歲做模特兒嘅連詩雅，以歌手身份出道，從不刻意賣弄性感，這張不經意嘅長腿加美臀照片，一樣睇到人好似佢首歌〈血一般紅〉咁，有幻想噴鼻血呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adBHpeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadBHpeE.jpg&h=bb353670&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7490235f0319141b33e62ee5cbdac13808fccba5","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":145,"score":-131,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"陳婉衡 30歲<br />\n<br />\n曾於旅遊節目如《 3日2夜 》、《 Go!Yama Girl 》中，展現震撼上圍，擁有健身教練牌照嘅佢亦熱愛瑜伽、鋼管舞，出晒名專操「 蜜桃臀 」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKz2peU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKz2peU.jpg&h=77dd423b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30701fc855a7b8de97f17aa911f365c4c18295f6","tid":2226562,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"整容樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d17f09eef32aaeb1aff037f23d35bdba18f38b","tid":2226562,"uid":44730,"like":99,"dislike":18,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:03:41.000Z","msg":"楊偲泳26歲<br />\n<br />\n擁有32D 上圍被冠以「 巨咪陳妍希 」嘅楊偲泳，同時亦係排球聯賽球員，下盤亦非常養眼，不時喺 IG 玩水著大放送，現任男友張振朗唔會呷醋吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i